Sonnentag Theatre at the IceHouse
1100 N Unser Street | Mount Dora, Florida 32757
1100 North Unser Street
Mount Dora, FL 32757
From the North and West, Leesburg & The Villages:
Take 441 South/East to Mount Dora.  At Lincoln Ave., turn Right at traffic light and left on Unser St. Proceed one block; the IceHouse is on the corner of 11th Ave. and Unser St.
From Orlando:
Take 441 north through Apopka. Continue North to Mount Dora, at Lincoln Ave., turn left at the traffic light and left onto Unser St. Proceed one block; the IceHouse is on the corner of 11th Ave. and Unser St.
From the 429:
take the Mount Dora exit then proceed on 441 North. At Lincoln Ave., turn left at the traffic light and left onto Unser St. Proceed one block; the IceHouse is on the corner of 11th Ave. and Unser St.
From the 453:
if you have missed the first exit for Mount Dora off of the 429, you can take the 453 to Rt 46. Proceed west on Rt 46 to 441. Take the 441 North about 1/4 mile to the traffic light at Lincoln Ave and turn left. Proceed one block; the IceHouse is on the corner of 11th Ave. and Unser St.
From I-4:
Take the exit at Sanford/Mount Dora. Take SR 46 West to Mount Dora and US 441 North about 1/4 mile to Lincoln Ave.  At Lincoln Ave., turn left at traffic light and left onto Unser St. Proceed one block; The IceHouse is on the corner of 11th Ave. and Unser St.
We Look Forward To Seeing You Soon!
Box Office: 352-383-4616
TO PURCHASE TICKETS: Go to the TICKETS MENU TAB / BUY TICKETS NOW on this site. Purchases can be made 24 hrs a day / 7 days a wk.
ON SHOW DATES: The lobby Box Office is open for Walk-In Sales an hour prior to the performance.
ON NON-SHOW DATES: The Box Office staff is working remotely with the phones being forwarded.
FOR TICKET PURCHASES AND INFO:  1:00 - 5:00 pm on Tues - Fri, is the best time to call.
If staff members are working with other patrons, your call will go to VoiceMail. Please leave a detailed msg.
You will be called back at our first opportunity that same day, or on the next business day.
You are welcome to email your questions and requests to INFO@ICEHOUSETHEATRE.COM; a response will be sent within 24-48 hours.
PATRON SERVICES: Alissa Pelkey, Box Office Manager
Sharlee Hollingsworth, Box Office Staff
